results.name: Number of non-isomorphic strict intersecting multiset partitions (sets of multisets) of weight n with empty intersection.
comment: A multiset partition is intersecting if no two parts are disjoint. The weight of a multiset partition is the sum of sizes of its parts. Weight is generally not the same as number of vertices.
